-- Zapatero Pledges Spain to Use All Tools to Prevent New Air-Traffic Strikes
-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 2010-12-09T09:41:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-09/zapatero-pledges-spain-to-use-all-tools-to-prevent-new-air-traffic-strikes.html
Prime Minister Jose Luis Rodriguez
Zapatero said the Spanish government “will not hesitate” to
use all the available legal tools to prevent a repeat of the
unofficial air-traffic controllers strike on Dec. 3. He spoke in
Parliament in Madrid today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  